---
title: Seared Salmon & Lemon Crushed Potatoes  with Rocket Salad & Herby Mayo
description: What’s better than a perfectly cooked, blushing pink salmon fillet? Trick question: nothing is! This flaky fish sits alongside a zesty crushed potato masterpiece - what a winning combo! Grab a fork and dig in.
